				<wikidot:authorName>Rioghail</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1302192</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>You could say that these articles&#8230; <em>are breeding like rabbits</em>. *dons sunglasses* [MUSIC EXPUNGED BY REQUEST OF TRACK RECORDS].</p> <p>On the other hand, this is adorable and I love the fact that there's nothing all that over-the-top about the anomaly. I'm not sure how I feel about the last 'event' and how it escalates the situation to include plane-crashes, but it's not enough to spoil the article. +1, my good chum.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
